# SettleUp Smart - Environment Variables

# Supabase Configuration
# Get these from your Supabase project dashboard at https://supabase.com/dashboard
# Project Settings > API > Project URL and Project API keys

# Your Supabase project URL
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-id.supabase.co

# Your Supabase anonymous public key (safe for client-side use)
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_supabase_anon_key_here

# Note: The anon key is designed to be exposed in client-side code.
# Security is handled through Row Level Security (RLS) policies in your database.
# Never expose your service_role key or database passwords!

# Email Configuration (Set in Supabase Dashboard)
# To make email verification look authentic:
# 1. Go to Authentication > Email Templates
# 2. Customize the "Confirm signup" template with SettleUp Smart branding
# 3. Set a legitimate sender address (no-reply@yourdomain.com)
# 4. If using a custom domain, set up proper SPF and DKIM records
